---
const target = '/maps/fishbread?admin=1';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="refresh" content={`0;url=${target}`} />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow" />
    <title>관리자 이동</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <script is:inline>
      window.location.replace('/maps/fishbread?admin=1');
    </script>
    <p>이동 중입니다. 자동 이동되지 않으면 <a href={target}>여기를 클릭</a>하세요.</p>
  </body>
</html>
